{"tid":861531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蝗禍】 杭州花海種咗3年，比抖音KOL用咗 3 日KO","createTime":"2018-10-14T08:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T17:46:27.000Z","uid":11598,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b94d46d92536bc4835511cb43efda8eeae38a38d","tid":861531,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T08:18:24.000Z","msg":"杭州濱江江邊公園裏，種着一大片「粉黛」，最近盛開形成大片粉紅色花海，優美的風景頻繁出現在抖音里，這裏也成了「網紅打卡地」，很多人都趕來拍照。<br />\n不過讓人遺憾的是，很多前來拍照的遊客肆意踐踏花海，原本站立挺直的「粉黛」，如今一大片一大片地被壓倒，讓人看着心疼。<br />\n據都市快報報道，這片花田大概佔地10畝，原本是一家婚慶公司的拍攝基地，粉黛草區域人氣最旺的地方，兩大片草堆中，密密麻麻全都是人，除了普通市民外，還有攝影師專門帶着模特趕過來的。<br />\n這片粉黛草由鄭阿姨和老伴兩個人看護，是澳大利亞進口來的，種植的時候非常小心，因爲它們一壓就倒，而且極易長蟲，辛辛苦苦種了3年，僅3天時間，就全被毀了。鄭阿姨說：「你們拍照片的人，拍出來的照片很美，可是你們的行爲卻很難看。」面對遊客的肆意毀壞，鄭阿姨已經聲帶發炎，老伴因爲勸阻他人踩花遭辱罵，一氣之下病倒了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/RKQWQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FRKQWQ.png&h=35c8b9d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/RKcUT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FRKcUT.png&h=3fd8cd3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6aa6a6d0edc17920f43e64825f785a993e83bdfd","tid":861531,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba8888056d79a269a4f288f721cc66afef9459d","tid":861531,"uid":35014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T08:20:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72cad62f3893a7c87bb31a55fe663ccf0f03b8a6","tid":861531,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T08:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2eefa7690ba19cbe16ec0a97840f166babff799","tid":861531,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:12:13.000Z","msg":"如果中國有槍既話<br />\n<br />\n園主 一槍一件蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99085ad482b5067b812fbdcfd615384d9c2400e8","tid":861531,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b288a1e34012c12f34f8c8b30c52456a113ca4","tid":861531,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T17:43:04.000Z","msg":"等睇「香港人咪又係咁」、「香港人仲離譜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3c877749c8cf2f893316599e60629d13d8af58","tid":861531,"uid":62226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"18b288a1e34012c12f34f8c8b30c52456a113ca4","tid":861531,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T17:43:04.000Z","msg":"等睇「香港人咪又係咁」、「香港人仲離譜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T17:46:27.000Z","msg":"全世界啲零零後都係咁"}]}